Explore Pixodesk SVG Animator Features

Powerful SVG animator that combines vector tools, intuitive animation features, and flexible export options.
Create vector graphics, add motion, and save them in lightweight formats optimized for production.

  • Create vector designs, apply animations, easing, effects, and export ready-to-use animations - all in one app.

  • Uses a globally supported SVG file format.

  • Animations will play in all browsers and web applications.

  • Supports multiple options for exporting your projects.

Create

  • Create or import vector drawings.

    Create your own SVG or import existing vector drawings.

  • Add images and custom TTF font.

    Import raster or vector images and use your own custom TTF fonts.

  • Make animation blocks.

    Use animation blocks to create detailed animated scenes.

Animate

  • Classic and auto-animation options.

    Use the Pin button to set the object's state on the canvas at one or more time points.

  • Pre-defined easing functions.

    Select them from a dropdown menu or adjust the easing curve by editing it.

  • Charts for speed and acceleration.

    These charts help you see how the changes happen over time.

Export

  • Save as SVG file.

    Export your vector file and add it to a portfolio, webpage, or social media platforms.

  • Export to different formats.

    You can export your animation as a video or GIF, or save static PNG, JPEG, WEBP, or SVG images at a certain time point.

  • Control how the animation begins and ends.

    In your application, you can decide whether the animation starts with a click, scroll, mouse movement, or other events.

Shape Builder Tool: From Simple to Sophisticated.

Merge, subtract, and manipulate shapes to create anything from icons to intricate illustrations.

  • Turn simple shapes into complex designs.

  • Build, merge, and adjust with ease.

  • Perfect for logos, illustrations, and more.

  • A must-have for every designer.

Animate Patterns, Markers & Spray: Add Depth to Your Designs

Create and animate custom patterns, markers, and spray to give your vector artwork extra dimension.

  • Animate custom Patterns.

  • Adjust colors, scale, or shape variations to create moving, dynamic pattern effects.

  • Animate your Marker designs.

  • Duplicate shapes along lines or paths and add motion for expressive animated details.

  • Create animated Spray effects.

  • Add motion to scattered shapes - great for particles, stars, snow, or creative textures.

Animated Vector Text

Easily animate text, apply effects over time, and move it along lines, waves, or geometric shapes.

  • Animate custom fonts that match your brand perfectly.

  • Animate text transforms using rotation, flip, scale, and other options.

  • Move text along any path or shape, animating start and offset positions.

  • Animate motion along closed shapes like circles and open shapes like lines or waves.

Auto-Animate: Automatically Animate Between States

A smart animation system that builds motion paths and property animations automatically.

  • The auto-animate feature takes care of keyframe creation.

  • Start by pinning the object's initial state.

  • Move to another time point and modify the object.

  • Your changes are instantly turned into keyframes.

Easing: Tools for Smoother Motion

Control pace and transitions using predefined easings, editable curves, and visual motion charts.

  • Add a realistic look to animations with predefined easing functions.

  • Easily change the easing curve to adjust the animation's feel.

  • See how changes affect speed and acceleration with built-in charts.

  • Mini velocity charts show how changes happen over time.

  • Easing charts show how the animation's speed and flow behave.

Create Animated Icons

Add personality and motion to your icons for web and apps.

  • Start with your icon - create one or import it from your library.

  • Animate it with rotation, scale, skew, Dash Array, or Trim Path.

  • Make it bounce, flip, fade, or move along a path.

  • Use snapping and grid options for precise placement.

Animated Repeater: Animate Multiple Elements at Once

Make complex patterns move with ease by animating all duplicates in one go.

  • Animate all properties of an entire set of elements at once.

  • Animate position, scale, rotation, and reference point (origin) for all duplicates from one place.

  • Tweak the source shape, and all duplicates update automatically.

  • Ensure symmetry and smooth motion while animating complex designs.
